<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bookstore - Checkout Done</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-GLhlTQ8iRABdZLl6O3oVMWSktQOp6b7In1Zl3/Jr59b6EGGoI1aFkw7cmDA6j6gD" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="fonts/fontawesome/css/all.css">
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar navbar-dark bg-dark">
      <div class="container">
          <a href="/" class="navbar-brand">Bookstore</a>
          <a href="/cart" class="navbar-text text-white">
              <span class="fw-bold">CART</span>
              <span class="px-2">/</span>
              <span class="fw-bold">${{totalPrice}}</span>
              <i class="fas fa-shopping-basket px-2"></i>
          </a>
      </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="container py-10">
    <div class="card mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title text-uppercase text-primary font-weight-bold">Спасибо за покупку!</h5>
        <p class="card-text mt-2 text-secondary">Общая стоимость: ${{totalPrice}}</p>
        <p class="card-text mt-2 text-secondary">Адрес доставки: {{address}}</p>
        <p class="card-text mt-2 text-secondary">Наша команда свяжется с вами в ближайшее время с дополнительной информацией о вашем заказе и доставке.</p>
        <p class="card-text mt-2 text-secondary">Ваш номер заказа: {{trackingNumber}}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-w76AqPfDkMBDXo30jS1Sgez6pr3x5MlQ1ZAGC+nuZB+EYdgRZgiwxhTBTkF7CXvN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>